w.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/06_bestial_exhibition_jaime_hayon_mingbeast_vase_ii_2024_mindy_solomon_gallery_ph_giovanni_ricco_yatzer.jpg\" width=\"1280\" height=\"1920\" alt=\"Jaime Hayon. \nMingbeast vase II, 2024. Acrylic and oil on canvas. 160 x 120 cm. \nPhotography by Giovanni Ricco.\nCourtesy of the artist and Mindy Solomon Gallery.\" title=\"Jaime Hayon. \nMingbeast vase II, 2024. Acrylic and oil on canvas. 160 x 120 cm. \nPhotography by Giovanni Ricco.\nCourtesy of the artist and Mindy Solomon Gallery.\" data-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/06_bestial_exhibition_jaime_hayon_mingbeast_vase_ii_2024_mindy_solomon_gallery_ph_giovanni_ricco_yatzer.jpg\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\n\n  \n      \u003cp\u003eJaime Hayon. \u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMingbeast vase II, 2024. \u003cbr/\u003eAcrylic and oil on canvas. \u003cbr/\u003e160 x 120 cm. \u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePhotography by Giovanni Ricco.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCourtesy of the artist and Mindy Solomon Gallery.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \n\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n  \n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \u003cfigure\u003e\n    \u003cimg data-original-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/07_bestial_exhibition_jaime_hayon_mingbeast_vase_ii_mindy_solomon_gallery_yatzer.jpg\" src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/07_bestial_exhibition_jaime_hayon_mingbeast_vase_ii_mindy_solomon_gallery_yatzer.jpg\" width=\"1280\" height=\"1812\" alt=\"Jaime Hayon. \nMingbeast vase II, 2024. Acrylic and oil on canvas. 160 x 120 cm. \nPhotography by Giovanni Ricco.\nCourtesy of the artist and Mindy Solomon Gallery.\" title=\"Jaime Hayon. \nMingbeast vase II, 2024. Acrylic and oil on canvas. 160 x 120 cm. \nPhotography by Giovanni Ricco.\nCourtesy of the artist and Mindy Solomon Gallery.\" data-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/07_bestial_exhibition_jaime_hayon_mingbeast_vase_ii_mindy_solomon_gallery_yatzer.jpg\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\n\n  \n      \u003cp\u003eJaime Hayon. \u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMingbeast vase II, 2024. \u003cbr/\u003eAcrylic and oil on canvas. \u003cbr/\u003e160 x 120 cm. \u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePhotography by Giovanni Ricco.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCourtesy of the artist and Mindy Solomon Gallery.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \n\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n  \n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n    \u003cp\u003eThe paintings on display are brimming with dynamic energy. A whirlwind of fantastical creatures leaps off the artist’s large canvases, while in smaller, still life paintings they are transformed into decorative elements. Underpinned by his perpetual search for self-understanding, Hayon’s troupe of kooky characters conveys a range of emotions, from fear and desire, to fragility and introspection. \u003cstrong\u003e“With this exhibition, I am returning to the origin of everything—the most visceral part of my work,” the artist reflects. “From the very depths of my being, I attempt to express my fantasy, my world, through painting—those free-flowing brushstrokes that naturally create the beastly forms of fauna and flora.”\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIn his still life paintings, Hayon contrasts luminous colours against shadowy or muted backdrops, an aesthetic inspired by ancient Egyptian art and Flemish flower paintings. This interplay between light and dark adds an emotional depth to the works while linking them to a broader artistic heritage. \u003cstrong\u003e“In Bestial, I highlight the crucial role animals have played in art history, symbolizing emotions and human experiences across civilizations,” Hayon explains. “From the Egyptians who humanized animals in their gods to artists like Picasso, Dalí, and Rousseau, animals have always expressed strength, rage, and passion.”\u003c/strong\u003e By drawing on these historical precedents, Hayon bridges past and present, using the natural world as a mirror for human emotion and societal critique.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n  \n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \u003cfigure\u003e\n    \u003cimg data-original-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/10_bestial_exhibition_jaime_hayon_bird_dutch_vase_2024_mindy_solomon_gallery_yatzer.jpg\" src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/10_bestial_exhibition_jaime_hayon_bird_dutch_vase_2024_mindy_solomon_gallery_yatzer.jpg\" width=\"1280\" height=\"1807\" alt=\"Jaime Hayon. \nBird Dutch vase, 2024. Acrylic and oil on canvas. 46 x 38 cm.\nPhotography by Giovanni Ricco.\nCourtesy of the artist and Mindy Solomon Gallery.\" title=\"Jaime Hayon. \nBird Dutch vase, 2024. Acrylic and oil on canvas. 46 x 38 cm.\nPhotography by Giovanni Ricco.\nCourtesy of the artist and Mindy Solomon Gallery.\" data-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/10_bestial_exhibition_jaime_hayon_bird_dutch_vase_2024_mindy_solomon_gallery_yatzer.jpg\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\n\n  \n      \u003cp\u003eJaime Hayon. \u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBird Dutch vase, 2024. \u003cbr/\u003eAcrylic and oil on canvas. \u003cbr/\u003e46 x 38 cm.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePhotography by Giovanni Ricco.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCourtesy of the artist and Mindy Solomon Gallery.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \n\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n  \n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \u003cfigure\u003e\n    \u003cimg data-original-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/08_bestial_exhibition_jaime_hayon_bird_dutch_vase_2024_mindy_solomon_gallery_ph_giovanni_ricco_yatzer.jpg\" src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/08_bestial_exhibition_jaime_hayon_bird_dutch_vase_2024_mindy_solomon_gallery_ph_giovanni_ricco_yatzer.jpg\" width=\"1280\" height=\"1641\" alt=\"Jaime Hayon. \nBird Dutch vase, 2024. Acrylic and oil on canvas. 46 x 38 cm. \nPhotography by Giovanni Ricco.\nCourtesy of the artist and Mindy Solomon Gallery.\" title=\"Jaime Hayon. \nBird Dutch vase, 2024. Acrylic and oil on canvas. 46 x 38 cm. \nPhotography by Giovanni Ricco.\nCourtesy of the artist and Mindy Solomon Gallery.\" data-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/08_bestial_exhibition_jaime_hayon_bird_dutch_vase_2024_mindy_solomon_gallery_ph_giovanni_ricco_yatzer.jpg\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\n\n  \n      \u003cp\u003eJaime Hayon. \u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBird Dutch vase, 2024. \u003cbr/\u003eAcrylic and oil on canvas. \u003cbr/\u003e46 x 38 cm. \u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePhotography by Giovanni Ricco.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCourtesy of the artist and Mindy Solomon Gallery.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \n\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n  \n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \u003cfigure\u003e\n    \u003cimg data-original-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/09_bestial_exhibition_jaime_hayon_bird_dutch_vase_2024_mindy_solomon_gallery_ph_giovanni_ricco_yatzer.jpg\" src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/09_bestial_exhibition_jaime_hayon_bird_dutch_vase_2024_mindy_solomon_gallery_ph_giovanni_ricco_yatzer.jpg\" width=\"1280\" height=\"1920\" alt=\"Jaime Hayon. \nBird Dutch vase, 2024. (Detail)Acrylic and oil on canvas. 46 x 38 cm. \nPhotography by Giovanni Ricco.\nCourtesy of the artist and Mindy Solomon Gallery.\" title=\"Jaime Hayon. \nBird Dutch vase, 2024. (Detail)Acrylic and oil on canvas. 46 x 38 cm. \nPhotography by Giovanni Ricco.\nCourtesy of the artist and Mindy Solomon Gallery.\" data-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/09_bestial_exhibition_jaime_hayon_bird_dutch_vase_2024_mindy_solomon_gallery_ph_giovanni_ricco_yatzer.jpg\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\n\n  \n      \u003cp\u003eJaime Hayon. \u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBird Dutch vase, 2024. (Detail)\u003cbr/\u003eAcrylic and oil on canvas. \u003cbr/\u003e46 x 38 cm. \u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePhotography by Giovanni Ricco.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCourtesy of the artist and Mindy Solomon Gallery.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \n\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n  \n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \u003cfigure\u003e\n    \u003cimg data-original-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/14_bestial_exhibition_jaime_hayon_mindy_solomon_gallery_ph_giovanni_ricco_yatzer.jpg\" src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/14_bestial_exhibition_jaime_hayon_mindy_solomon_gallery_ph_giovanni_ricco_yatzer.jpg\" width=\"1280\" height=\"1920\" alt=\"Photography by Giovanni Ricco.\nCourtesy of the artist and Mindy Solomon Gallery.\" title=\"Photography by Giovanni Ricco.\nCourtesy of the artist and Mindy Solomon Gallery.\" data-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/14_bestial_exhibition_jaime_hayon_mindy_solomon_gallery_ph_giovanni_ricco_yatzer.jpg\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\n\n  \n      \u003cp\u003ePhotography by Giovanni Ricco.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCourtesy of the artist and Mindy Solomon Gallery.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \n\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n  \n\n\n  \n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \u003cfigure\u003e\n    \u003cimg data-original-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/13_bestial_exhibition_jaime_hayon_beast_i_2024_mindy_solomon_gallery_ph_giovanni_ricco_yatzer.jpg\" src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/13_bestial_exhibition_jaime_hayon_beast_i_2024_mindy_solomon_gallery_ph_giovanni_ricco_yatzer.jpg\" width=\"1280\" height=\"1920\" alt=\"Jaime Hayon. \nBeast I, 2024.  Acrylic and oil on canvas. 250 x 130 cm. \nPhotography by Giovanni Ricco.\nCourtesy of the artist and Mindy Solomon Gallery.\" title=\"Jaime Hayon. \nBeast I, 2024.  Acrylic and oil on canvas. 250 x 130 cm. \nPhotography by Giovanni Ricco.\nCourtesy of the artist and Mindy Solomon Gallery.\" data-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/13_bestial_exhibition_jaime_hayon_beast_i_2024_mindy_solomon_gallery_ph_giovanni_ricco_yatzer.jpg\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\n\n  \n      \u003cp\u003eJaime Hayon. \u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBeast I, 2024.  \u003cbr/\u003eAcrylic and oil on canvas. \u003cbr/\u003e250 x 130 cm. \u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePhotography by Giovanni Ricco.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCourtesy of the artist and Mindy Solomon Gallery.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \n\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n  \n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n    \u003cp\u003eComplementing the paintings, Hayon’s sculptures translate his surreal visions into three-dimensional forms. Working with materials such as glass and fiberglass, \u003cstrong\u003ehe transforms his whimsical characters into tactile objects that invite closer examination, further developing the themes of hybridization and interconnectedness, creating a cohesive narrative across mediums.\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMore than a visual feast, Bestial offers a whimsical yet profound meditation on the connections—and disconnections—between humanity and the environment, inviting viewers to embrace the unknown, explore their own emotions, and reimagine the world through his uniquely playful perspective.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n  \n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \u003cfigure\u003e\n    \u003cimg data-original-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/15_bestial_exhibition_jaime_hayon_totem_land_murano_2023_mindy_solomon_gallery_courtesy_l21_yatzer.jpg\" src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/15_bestial_exhibition_jaime_hayon_totem_land_murano_2023_mindy_solomon_gallery_courtesy_l21_yatzer.jpg\" width=\"1280\" height=\"1918\" alt=\"Jaime Hayon. \nTotem land Murano I, 2023.Murano handblowed glass. 100 x 50 x 40 cm. \nCourtesy L21.\" title=\"Jaime Hayon. \nTotem land Murano I, 2023.Murano handblowed glass. 100 x 50 x 40 cm. \nCourtesy L21.\" data-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/15_bestial_exhibition_jaime_hayon_totem_land_murano_2023_mindy_solomon_gallery_courtesy_l21_yatzer.jpg\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\n\n  \n      \u003cp\u003eJaime Hayon. \u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTotem land Murano I, 2023.\u003cbr/\u003eMurano handblowed glass. \u003cbr/\u003e100 x 50 x 40 cm. \u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCourtesy L21.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \n\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n  \n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \u003cfigure\u003e\n    \u003cimg data-original-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/16_bestial_exhibition_jaime_hayon_mindy_solomon_gallery_ph_giovanni_ricco_yatzer.jpg\" src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/16_bestial_exhibition_jaime_hayon_mindy_solomon_gallery_ph_giovanni_ricco_yatzer.jpg\" width=\"1280\" height=\"1920\" alt=\"Jaime Hayon. \nTotem land Murano II, 2023. Murano handblowed glass. \nPhotography by Giovanni Ricco.\nCourtesy of the artist and Mindy Solomon Gallery.\" title=\"Jaime Hayon. \nTotem land Murano II, 2023. Murano handblowed glass. \nPhotography by Giovanni Ricco.\nCourtesy of the artist and Mindy Solomon Gallery.\" data-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/16_bestial_exhibition_jaime_hayon_mindy_solomon_gallery_ph_giovanni_ricco_yatzer.jpg\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\n\n  \n      \u003cp\u003eJaime Hayon. \u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTotem land Murano II, 2023. \u003cbr/\u003eMurano handblowed glass. \u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePhotography by Giovanni Ricco.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCourtesy of the artist and Mindy Solomon Gallery.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \n\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n  \n\n\n  \n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \u003cfigure\u003e\n    \u003cimg data-original-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/11_bestial_exhibition_jaime_hayon_mindy_solomon_gallery_yatzer.jpg\" src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/11_bestial_exhibition_jaime_hayon_mindy_solomon_gallery_yatzer.jpg\" width=\"1280\" height=\"1920\" alt=\"Jaime Hayon at his studio.\nPhotography by Giovanni Ricco.\nCourtesy of the artist and Mindy Solomon Gallery.\" title=\"Jaime Hayon at his studio.\nPhotography by Giovanni Ricco.\nCourtesy of the artist and Mindy Solomon Gallery.\" data-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/11_bestial_exhibition_jaime_hayon_mindy_solomon_gallery_yatzer.jpg\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\n\n  \n      \u003cp\u003eJaime Hayon at his studio.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePhotography by Giovanni Ricco.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCourtesy of the artist and Mindy Solomon Gallery.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \n\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n  \n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \u003cfigure\u003e\n    \